# Testing Twigs Component Library Rules

## Available Components

Use components from `testing-twigs` package instead of raw React Native components.

### Layout Components
```typescript
import { Flex, Box } from 'testing-twigs';

// Flex - flexbox layout container
<Flex 
  direction="row" | "column" | "row-reverse" | "column-reverse"
  justify="flex-start" | "flex-end" | "center" | "space-between" | "space-around"
  align="flex-start" | "flex-end" | "center" | "stretch"
  wrap="nowrap" | "wrap" | "wrap-reverse"
  padding={16}
  margin={8}
  css={{ backgroundColor: '#fff' }}
/>

// Box - container with spacing utilities
<Box 
  padding={16}
  paddingHorizontal={24}
  paddingVertical={12}
  margin={16}
  marginTop={8}
  css={{ backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5' }}
/>
```

